WEBVTT

00:02:59.880 --> 00:03:01.296
30 yoshda edim.

00:03:01.320 --> 00:03:03.696
Yo’q, o’sha kompaniyani qurmadim.

00:03:03.720 --> 00:03:05.256
Hatto boshladim ham.

00:03:05.280 --> 00:03:09.256
Men o'zi Fortune 500 kompaniyalaridan
birida marketing menejer bo'lib ishlardim.

00:03:09.280 --> 00:03:10.896
Bir yerda turib qolganimni bildim.

00:03:10.920 --> 00:03:12.120
Bir yerda qotib qoldim.

00:03:13.080 --> 00:03:14.296
Nega?

00:03:14.320 --> 00:03:16.560
O’sha xatni yozgan 14 yoshli bola qani?

00:03:17.480 --> 00:03:18.957
Bunga sabab uning urinib

00:03:19.480 --> 00:03:22.536
ko’rmaganligi emas.
Bunga sabab har safar menda yangi g'oya

00:03:22.560 --> 00:03:24.536
uyg’onganida, biror 
yangi narsaga urinib

00:03:24.560 --> 00:03:25.776
ko’rishni istaganimda,

00:03:25.800 --> 00:03:27.536
hatto ishda ham taklif berishni

00:03:27.560 --> 00:03:31.096
istardim guruhda odamlar orasida
o’z fikrimni bildirishni istardim